{"tid":1912130,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"50+1點解？球隊數目？","createTime":"2020-03-05T23:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T04:51:26.000Z","uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a83dc05619936b3eed63586a25359f17952af850","tid":1912130,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T23:25:44.000Z","msg":"咩黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"258745fe55d362cdc76fd1ab37fe9e1e859acb30","tid":1912130,"uid":235475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T23:27:09.000Z","msg":"年紀呀"},{"pid":"0249ae9f0e87670988179e9d0e361f9e263b9b9b","tid":1912130,"uid":66368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T23:29:26.000Z","msg":"問google"},{"pid":"500a36fbec29e037cd235fbd68dd12680ef275f6","tid":1912130,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"258745fe55d362cdc76fd1ab37fe9e1e859acb30","tid":1912130,"uid":235475,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T23:27:09.000Z","msg":"年紀呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T23:32:34.000Z","msg":"即係51歲以上唔準教波？"},{"pid":"6a0ef7d0164793ed581a2f6b7c66a5284fb02626","tid":1912130,"uid":87793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T00:04:01.000Z","msg":"50+1制度可以說是德國足球的特別之處，簡單來說，在德國註冊的球會，該球會的球迷會員的投票權必須過半數，換句說話，球迷會員決定了球會的政策能否通過，這個政策的目的是希望德國的球會不會成為「金主」的玩具，並確保球迷和球會的關係，希望保持足球沿於人民的理念。然而在這個政策中，有一條豁免條例，就是假如一個人或企業連續經營球會超過20年，他就可以不受50+1制度的限制，完全擁有這間球會，而賀普就是經營了賀芬咸20年獲豁免的人。"},{"pid":"575cb900f585dcc64828c7930708942afc03a061","tid":1912130,"uid":11389,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T04:51:26.000Z","msg":"可以睇下哩度 解釋得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.wisdompocket.com/?p=1032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wisdompocket.com%2F%3Fp%3D1032&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcHlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=11f3b55b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.wisdompocket.com/?p=1032</a>"}]}